The paper focuses on image feature extraction using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a new method for feature learning, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The method is based on fuzzy rules, which is a type of neural network (cs.NE) and can be applied to information retrieval (cs.IR). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, and cs.IR.
